Accessibility'),(244,35,'_features_2_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(245,35,'features_2_body','Everyone should be able to use, perceive, and interact with your website regardless of their abilities or disabilities. Deliver optimized content for assistive technologies and provide a great experience for users of all life circumstances. Your website will meet or exceed <i>WCAG 2.0 Level AA</i> as required by the <i>Accessibility for Ontarians with Disabilities Act, 2005</i>.'),(246,35,'_features_2_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(247,35,'features_3_icon','fa-github fa-fw'),(248,35,'_features_3_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(249,35,'features_3_heading','Source Code Management'),(250,35,'_features_3_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(251,35,'features_3_body','Your websiteâs code will be version controlled so that each edit and its details are logged. Code can be reverted to any previous state, and multiple developers can coordinate and merge their work with ease. Your source code is the magic that makes your website a reality. Version control helps prevent disasters and allows quick recovery.'),(252,35,'_features_3_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(253,35,'features_4_icon','fa-cubes fa-fw'),(254,35,'_features_4_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(255,35,'features_4_heading','Multi-Tier Deployments'),(256,35,'_features_4_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(257,35,'features_4_body','New or revised code is deployed to a testing site where it must pass all tests and be approved before it goes into the live site. This structured release process reduces risks, enables simple rollbacks, and allows phased release rollouts. Catch bugs before your users see them and prevent downtime due to human error.'),(258,35,'_features_4_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(259,35,'features_5_icon','fa-line-chart fa-fw'),(260,35,'_features_5_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(261,35,'features_5_heading','Analytics'),(262,35,'_features_5_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(263,35,'features_5_body','Information that helps you