74441c90aa'),(1177,123,'features_1_heading','Device Agnostic'),(1178,123,'_features_1_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1179,123,'features_1_body','Fully responsive design that adapts to the users screen size. Your website will make the best use of available screen real estate and deliver your users an experience optimized for their device.'),(1180,123,'_features_1_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1181,123,'features_2_icon','fa-universal-access fa-fw'),(1182,123,'_features_2_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1183,123,'features_2_heading','Accessibility'),(1184,123,'_features_2_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1185,123,'features_2_body','Everyone should be able to use, perceive, and interact with your website regardless of their abilities or disabilities. Deliver optimized content for assistive technologies and provide a great experience for users of all life circumstances. Your website will meet or exceed <i>WCAG 2.0 Level AA</i> as required by the <i>Accessibility for Ontarians with Disabilities Act, 2005</i>.'),(1186,123,'_features_2_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1187,123,'features_3_icon','fa-github fa-fw'),(1188,123,'_features_3_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1189,123,'features_3_heading','Source Code Management'),(1190,123,'_features_3_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1191,123,'features_3_body','Your websiteâs code will be version controlled so that each edit and its details are logged. Code can be reverted to any previous state, and multiple developers can coordinate and merge their work with ease. Your source code is the magic that makes your website a reality. Version control helps prevent disasters and allows quick recovery.'),(1192,123,'_features_3_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1193,123,'features_4_icon','fa-cubes fa-fw'),(1194,123,'_features_4_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1195,123,'features_4_heading','Multi-Tier Deployments'),(1196,123,'_features_4_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1197,123,'features_4_body','New or revised code is deployed to a testing site where it must pass all tests and be approved before it goes into the live site. This structured release process reduces risks, enables simple rollbacks, and allows phased release rollouts. Catch bugs before your users see them and prevent downtime due to human error.'),(1198,123,'_features_4_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1199,123,'features_5_icon','fa-line-chart fa-fw'),(1200,123,'_features_5_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1201,123,'features_5_heading','Analytics'),(1202,123,'_features_5_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1203,123,'features_5_body','Information that helps you learn how people use your website, and where they are from. Make evidence based decisions that improve your website to provide users with more value and a better experience. Your website will integrate with Google Analytics so that you always have the best information.'),(1204,123,'_features_5_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1205,123,'features','6'),(1206,123,'_features','field_5a474441c90a9'),(1207,123,'quote_bar_body','\"The original idea of the web was that it should be a collaborative space where you can communicate through sharing information.\"'),(1208,123,'_quote_bar_body','field_5a47459b6956d'),(1209,123,'quote_bar_cite','- Tim Berners-Lee'),(1210,123,'_quote_bar_cite','field_5a4745d46956e'),(1211,123,'quote_bar',''),(1212,123,'_quote_bar','field_5a4745776956c'),(1213,123,'cost_heading','\"OK, so how much does it cost?\"'),(1214,123,'_cost_heading','field_5a4764d9370f2'),(1215,123,'cost_body','It depends and varies based on requirements. I provide free consultancy to learn what you want to accomplish and provide sensible options to make it happen. Then you get a quote based on the information I learn from this discovery phase. I wish it was easier, but making up numbers serves nobody and would be misleading.'),(1216,123,'_cost_body','field_5a4764e7370f3'),(1217,123,'cost_cta','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"Give me a shout and letâs get started\";s:3:\"url\";s:30:\"http://derulski.local/contact/\